# Unknown functions

##nagelfar syntax - x x*
##nagelfar syntax + x*

# Pdf4Tcl's source uses "throw" for errors. This disallows other ways.
##nagelfar syntax error 0
##nagelfar syntax return r 0 1

##nagelfar package known tiff
##nagelfar syntax tiff::isTIFF x
##nagelfar syntax tiff::getEntry x x

